        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>You have trained to use your fists as deadly weapons. The damage die for your fist unarmed attacks becomes [[/r 1d6]] instead of [[/r 1d4]]. You don't take the -2 circumstance penalty for making a lethal attack with your nonlethal unarmed attacks.</p>\n<p>Whenever you gain a class feature that grants you expert or greater proficiency in certain weapons, you also gain that proficiency rank in all unarmed attacks.</p>\n<p><strong>Special</strong> You can't select another dedication feat until you have gained two other feats from the martial artist archetype.</p>"
